    "body": "Hey, after a discussion, we decided to make this a bit more simple and remove the drag-and-drop and replace it with just taps.\r\n\r\nHere's a video with how it should look:  https://www.dropbox.com/s/tpqc1sihu8xjdny/backup.mov?dl=0\r\n\r\nHere are some notable things:\r\n- you can select only one word at a time by tapping on it;\r\n- if you have already selected a word and then tapped on another one, the other one gets selected;\r\n- if you tap on an already selected word, it gets deselected;\r\n- the error is shown for 1200 ms;\r\n- the successful frame stays and the word disappears  if placed correctly;\r\n- after an error is shown, the currently selected word gets deselected",
